quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  72,1,"Maaku : \"Wahayinaama e am, wonnde dental jinna he…óino [lam mi…óo jannga Alqur'aana], …ói wi'i: \"Menen men nani janngeteende haawniinde"
  72,2,"Hinde …óowira e peewal. Men gom…óinii nde. Men kafidatah e Joomi amen, hay e gooto"
  72,3,"E wonnde manngural Joomi amen ngal mawnii, O siforaali jogitagol genndo, wanaa …ďi…ó…óo"
  72,4,"E wonnde [Ibuliisa] …óay…óo on e amen hino wowlaynoo penaale e hoore Allah"
  72,5,Menen men sikkuno wonnde yim…ďe e jinna wowlataano fenaande e hoore Allah
  72,6,"Hari le wor…ďe yim…ďe hino mooloraynoo wor…ďe jinna, …ďe …ďeydi …ói bewre"
  72,7,"Kam…ďe [yim…ďe …ďen] …ďe sikkir no sikkir…óon non, wonnde Allah immintintah hay gooto"
  72,8,"E wonnde men meemii kammu ngun, men tawi hingu hebbiniraa aynoo…ďe tii…óu…ďe e docote"
  72,9,"E wonnde me…óen joo…óotonoo ton fii he…óagol. Kala non he…óitii…óo jooni, o hawray e docotal tommbingal"
  72,10,"E wonnde men anndaa si ko bone faandanaa won…ďe ka leydi …ďen, kaa hara Joomi ma…ď…ďe faandani …ďe peewal"
  72,11,"E wonnde hino e amen mo∆ī∆īu…ói, hino e amen kadi ko jaasi …óum. Hari me…óen e laawi seertu…ói"
  72,12,"E wonnde men fellituno men laawotaako Allah ka hoore leydi, e wonnde men laawortaa Mo dogugol"
  72,13,"E wonnde nde men nanunoo peewal nagl, men gom…óini ngal. Kala gom…óin…óo Joomi mun, on hulataa …óuytaneede [mo∆ī∆īi] wanaa …ďeydaneede [bon…ói]"
  72,14,"E wonnde hino e amen jebbilii…ói, hino e amen kadi oo√Īii…ói. Kala jebbilii ngii, …óin …óon faandike peewal"
  72,15,"Oo√Īii…ói …óin kan, …ói laatanike Jahannama on carmalle"
  72,16,"E wonnde si …ďe √Īii…ďuno e hoore laawol ngol, ko pellet, Men yarnayno …ďe ndiyam …óuu…óu…óam"
  72,17,"fii yo Men ndaarndoro …ďe heen. Kala …óuurnii…óo e jantoore Joomi mun nden, O naaday mo e lette sattu…óe"
  72,18,E wonnde juulir…óe …óen ko Allah heeranii. Wata on kafidu e Allah hay e gooto
  72,19,"E wonnde tuma jeyaa…óo Allah on darinoo himo rewa Mo, …ói …óe…ďuno wa…ó…óondirgol e hoore makko"
  72,20,"Maaku : \"Anndee ko Joomi am (tun) mi rewata, mi kafidataa Mo kadi hay e gooto"
  72,21,"Maaku : \"Min on mi waawanaa on du√Īude lorra, wanaa fii poo…óugol nafa"
  72,22,"Maaku : \"Hay gooto waawaa da…óndugol lam e Allah; mi he…ďataa ko woori Mo ∆īoo√Īorde"
  72,23,"si wanaa yottingol immorde e Allah e nule Makko …óen. Kala yeddu…óo Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, haray ko Yiite Jahannama woodani mo, …ďe luttay e magge poomaa"
  72,24,"Haa si …ďe yi'ii ko …ďe kammbirananoo kon, …ďe aray anndude ko hombo …ďuri lo'ude ballo, …ďuri kadi fan…óude limoore"
  72,25,"Maaku : \"Mi anndaa si ko kammbirana…óon kon hino …ďadii, maa si Joomi am wa…óanay …óum dumunna"
  72,26,Ko O ganndo wirnii…ói. O ∆īellintinantaa wirnii…ói Makko …óin hay e gooto
  72,27,"si wanaa mo O welanaa e Nulaa…óo, O naadnay yeeso on e …ďaawo makko tommbotoo…ďe"
  72,28,"fii yo o anndu wonnde …ďen yottinii nule Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óen. O hu…ďindorii (anndugol) ko woni ka ma…ď…ďe kon, O mofti limoore kala huunde"